<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>ذِكْرُ أَحْكَامِ أَطْفَالِهِمْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَفِيهِ بَابَانِ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الْبَابُ الْأَوَّلُ:</span> فِي ذِكْرِ أَحْكَامِهِمْ فِي الدُّنْيَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَالْبَابُ الثَّانِي:</span> فِي ذِكْرِ أَحْكَامِهِمْ فِي الْآخِرَةِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>